<h2>Recovery &amp; Redemption</h2>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Explore what the bible says about addiction and recovery. You will hear personal stories of struggle and hope, do the 12 steps from a biblical perspective, and receive support.</p>
<p class="noPspace">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Thursdays: May 1 - July 24</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">6:30-8:30pm at Crossroads Florence</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.crossroads.net/my/signup/2003509">Sign up here</a><a href="http://www.crossroads.net/my/signup/2003222" target="_blank">.</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>CHILDCARE</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">If you make a reservation one week in advance, childcare is available for nursery through fifth grade in Kids&rsquo; Club.</p>
